{"title":"西藏行（二首）","authors":["晓雪"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":11,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在冰山雪海之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片洁白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个银亮亮的水晶世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四方是一道道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶莹璀璨的耀眼的光芒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八面来风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都那么清新、凉爽、畅快；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我几乎睁不开眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中却一阵狂喜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来到了多年向往的、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次梦中见到的雪域。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，也许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这才是我的故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的灵魂的归宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的生命的起点……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉萨的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小学叫雪小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市叫雪城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布达拉宫周围的百姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都自称为“雪”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到新奇、绝妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而又无比亲切！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯洁、朴素、白净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶莹、璀璨、辉煌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既普普通通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又光彩照人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既能凝成冰川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古不化，照耀蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又可化为春水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润万物，使草绿花开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，拉萨的雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是这个城市的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是它的希望和未来。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}